 "remarks": "Quietly iconic. Effortlessly cool. Live large without living complicated. This is the rare waterfront home that offers the lifestyle of a grand estate with the ease of a true lock-and-leave retreat. Set on just over an acre in the private Tokeneke Association it&apos;s designed for living well not maintaining endlessly. There are four private bedrooms in the main house and several places to lounge. Escape whenever you choose a weekend, a week, or all the days in between. Paddle over to Rowayton for lunch, entertain under the stars by the fire, or spend an afternoon with a great book by the pool. A private guest cottage with multiple sleep configurations offers family and friends their own retreat while preserving yours. Waterfront homes that live this effortlessly are incredibly rare. A manageable home, beautiful grounds, a dock, freeform pool, an abundant vegetable garden and even a chicken coop, all within the security of Tokeneke including optional home check-ins while you&apos;re away. Make coming and going completely carefree, an easy house, an extraordinary life.",
